        "text": "IN HIS POSSESSION CONCERNING THE STATEMENTS SET OUT HEREIN.\nHOOVER\nFBI:CMW\nRECORDED - 59\nINDEXED - 59\n162-8894-193\nFBI\nAUG 10 1949\nINITIATED\nDIRECTOR'S OFFICE\nRECEIVED\nJUL 12 4 38 PM '49\nFEDERAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION\nU. S. DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE\nCOMMUNICATIONS SECTION\nCOPIES DESTROYED\nNOV 18 1964\nJUL 12 1949\nAUG 11 1949\nTELEME TER\nSENT VIA\nPER"
      },
